Correct Ans: `ggplot(tble, aes(x=category, y=count)) + geom_bar(stat='identity')`. The default behaviour of `geom_bar()` automatically counts value and requires only x aesthetic i.e. `ggplot(tble, aes(x=category)) + geom_bar()`. #RStats #DataScience [TimeStamp:11092021220018] https://t.co/I5nhOWWgt2
